window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Just when I thought I'd finally found happiness, the nightmare I've been running from finds me, and my world goes dark.</b></p> <p>Taking more from me than one person should ever have to lose, I end up on a new path, discovering I'm capable of things I never imagined possible, not even in the darkest parts of my imagination.</p> <p>So much blood. So much pain. So. Much. Death.</p> <p>Now, in a world where right is wrong, and the means justify the ends, where my presence brings destruction and devastation, I need to find my way back to the light, to joy. To love.</p> <p>I thought when trouble came for me, I'd need the biggest monsters of the city on my side... but it turns out when you come for the people I love, I might be the biggest monster of all.</p> <p><i>Intended for mature listeners.</i></p>"; 
